{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e0130af52c","title":"辩证法的要素（摘自《黑格尔<逻辑学>一书摘要》）","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"70ceefa14f","index":1,"year":1914,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"a2a51d1cf4","index":0,"year":1914,"month":9,"day":null,"articleId":"e0130af52c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","name":"列宁选集 第二卷（1972年）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"列宁，人民出版社1972年","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"b353e6fb43","name":"列宁"}]},"publication_details":{"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9c7648b8ec","type":"paragraph","text":"辩证法的要素","index":0,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"b3c873c3d7","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自《黑格尔《逻辑学>一书摘要》）（1）观察的客观性（不是实例，不是枝节之论，辩证法的要素","index":1,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"df87254f1c","type":"paragraph","text":"而是自在之物本身）。","index":2,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"ce52748258","type":"paragraph","text":"X（2）这个事物对其他事物的多种多样的关系","index":3,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"0a7f80949b","type":"paragraph","text":"的全部总和。（3）这个事物（或现象）的发展、它自身的运动、","index":4,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"65f55196b0","type":"paragraph","text":"它自身的生命。（4）这个事物中的内在矛盾的倾向（和方面）。","index":5,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"ff46650884","type":"paragraph","text":"特（5）事物（现象等等）是对立面的总和与统一（6）这些对立面，矛盾的超向等等的斗争或展","index":6,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"c4753d6a15","type":"paragraph","text":"开。（7）分析和综合的结合，——各个部分的分解","index":7,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"c0bef0fcc3","type":"paragraph","text":"和所有这些部分的总和、总计。（8）每个事物（现象等等）的关系不仅是多种多X样的，并且是一般的、普遍的。每个事物（现象、过程等等）是和其他的每个事物联系着的。（9）不仅是对立面的统一，而且是每个规定，","index":8,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"5b0cfcc4f1","type":"paragraph","text":"质、特征、方面、特性向每个他者一向自己","index":9,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"3384de28a3","type":"paragraph","text":"的对立面？的转化。（10）揭露新的方面、关系等等的无限过程。（11）人对事物、现象、过程等等的认识从现象到","index":10,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"4eb5a2b9c4","type":"paragraph","text":"本质、从不甚深刻的本质到更深刻的本质","index":11,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"bac2bd3ed6","type":"paragraph","text":"的深化的无限过程（12）从并存到因果性以及从联系和相互依存的","index":12,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"c961bb2740","type":"paragraph","text":"一个形式到另一个更深刻更一般的形式。（13）在高级阶段上重复低级阶段的某些特征、","index":13,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"26b3bfe1e7","type":"paragraph","text":"特性等等，并且（14）仿佛是向旧东西的回复（否定的）","index":14,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"0ae237204c","type":"paragraph","text":"（否定（15）内容和形式以及形式和内容的斗争。抛弃","index":15,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"32cc7e4b3d","type":"paragraph","text":"形式、改造内容。（16）从量到质和从质到量的转化。（（15和16","index":16,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"727671a24d","type":"paragraph","text":"是9的实例））","index":17,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"feb0f62ed5","type":"paragraph","text":"可以把辩证法简要地确定为关于对立面的统一的学说。这样就会抓住辩证法的核心，可是这需要说明和发挥。","index":18,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"97dba3cd0e","type":"paragraph","text":"有写于1914年9月-12月","index":19,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"75625cf9bf","type":"paragraph","text":"按手稿刊印","index":20,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"bd7be89e9c","type":"paragraph","text":"选自《列宁全集》第38卷1929年第一次载于《列宁文集》","index":21,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"},{"id":"39637fbed3","type":"paragraph","text":"第238-240页第9卷","index":22,"publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c"}],"page":{"id":"f10183b4a7","publicationId":"f9ee796e-86d1-06cd-8329-046ef5b033f2","articleId":"e0130af52c","start":620,"end":621}}}},"__N_SSG":true}